Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.80,0:00:05.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚少年  鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.27,0:00:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有两个力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.47,0:00:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一个是Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:12.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对任何对手都能下令使其绝对服从的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.66,0:00:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一个是黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为破坏父亲统治的布里塔尼亚的他自己的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.51,0:00:24.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修借ZERO这个代号行动起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.30,0:00:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了替母亲报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.50,0:00:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有为了创造妹妹娜娜莉能幸福生活的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.51,0:00:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这行动会导致怎样的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.50,0:00:39.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在谁也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.12,0:02:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,395)}STAGE 9
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,430)}Refrain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.13,0:02:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,河口的会议中心宾馆终于开始重建工程了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO宣布黑色骑士团以来已经两周以上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结果还是没有找到确实的证据吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:27.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,逃走路线被隐蔽起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.53,0:02:30.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,解放人质还有引导车辆到海岸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.90,0:02:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.53,0:02:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.46,0:02:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  吵醒你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.79,0:02:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.86,0:02:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  这次是梯子倒下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.09,0:02:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快收拾干净
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就是去学校的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:02:57.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐  最近您经常去学校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.06,0:02:59.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是交上了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.25,0:03:00.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这和你没有关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:17.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是福利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.35,0:03:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是把这东西给11区人实在是太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才流到你们那儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么  11区人减少一点才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,报酬就汇到你太太的户头上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.93,0:03:33.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,科奈莉娅殿下是武人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.16,0:03:36.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对这种东西不会熟悉的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:42.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,灯  快打开灯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:04:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真少见  卡莲居然会打瞌睡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  稍微有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:04.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你干脆做鲁路修的徒弟算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.88,0:04:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是打瞌睡的强者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是在打瞌睡么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都不知道他每天晚上在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙上课有一半时间都在睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:20.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在埃洛拉主战线EU发动了攻势
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.97,0:04:20.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[Ellora：印度孟买东北部小村庄，今名贝鲁莱]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从我们的角度说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能一直被这个11区给绊住手脚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.42,0:04:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要把内政处理干净  让那边升格为安全地区
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说为了这些  击溃恐怖组织也是重要的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但在11区中蔓延的药物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Refrain的问题也很严峻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.11,0:04:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这个  生产力也下降了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要把中华联邦的主输送线给截断
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:44.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  请务必小心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:49.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是  别再从租界出去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.86,0:04:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  关于黑色骑士团的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们再逍遥法外一段时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.05,0:04:57.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也欠他们救你这个情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:04:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是等我回来后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.29,0:05:06.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会把这个区弄干净了再交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不要想危险的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.36,0:05:10.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗  由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.32,0:05:14.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.82,0:05:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是布里塔尼亚皇帝的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.84,0:05:18.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:24.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  现在还…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候ZERO说的话的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.92,0:05:31.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是指还会继续呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:32.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是你的话会怎么想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对于ZERO的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.74,0:05:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  我会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.72,0:05:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是辛苦啊  二重生活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  朱雀  那边那边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:50.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  住手啊朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.94,0:05:52.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手  快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:53.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是会长命令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.40,0:05:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的脸明明在笑啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:58.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好喵~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:03.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早…上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦  没有和你说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:08.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿瑟的欢迎会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.75,0:06:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真和平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:13.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,危机期间就好好享受嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.98,0:06:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也准备了卡莲的份
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.83,0:06:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作为上次我对你说了奇怪的话的道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.03,0:06:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要哪件?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  我也要?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:22.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲就不需要了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:25.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早就带着(假面)了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么不上电视
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:30.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会很受欢迎的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:32.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么看  电视明星小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  话题转移到那边啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要开这种玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.59,0:06:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后我们可辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,每时每刻都被人围着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.84,0:06:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,逼着追问问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,连在澡堂里也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这一个礼拜连学校都出不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:50.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这样  为什么连我们也要禁止外出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就叫友情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不求同日而生 只求同日而死  By~三国志
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:07:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[引自三国志中桃园结义时的话 原文为不求同年同月同日生 只愿同年同月同日死]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这难道是在求婚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.32,0:07:02.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要死也要拖人下水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你真过分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:04.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家又能在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.17,0:07:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这时候应该笑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但这就是朱雀的优点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,希望他偶尔也能考虑一下周围的气氛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.30,0:07:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.60,0:07:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊  那只不过是开玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:31.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  我救了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,宾馆劫持事件华丽登场之后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,世界的目光集中在黑色骑士团身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:43.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色骑士团正如ZERO的宣言般是弱者的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:45.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不把平民卷进来的恐怖行动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蛮横的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.93,0:07:48.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有贪污的政治家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.60,0:07:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,盈利主义至上的企业
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:52.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,犯罪组织之类的法律无法惩治的邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,单方面进行制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.19,0:07:58.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们瞬间就成了英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,协助者也增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也再次得到了KnightMare
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但并不都只是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.60,0:08:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要玩这个了  黑色骑士团这种
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能说布里塔尼亚的坏话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.62,0:08:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可是11区住民啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.11,0:08:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,首领的ZERO杀了克洛维斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.07,0:08:22.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴间想要知道他真实面目的人也很多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是总觉得如果强逼他的话他就会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:32.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或许现在已到了他不在就不行的地步了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对我们来说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说最近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很少陪我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.60,0:08:39.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.23,0:08:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.81,0:08:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么民众会帮助救了由菲米娅的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:09:00.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,京都也说要把红莲二式交给黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.26,0:09:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给那种半吊子?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他们根本不是反抗组织
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,证据就是他们杀了草壁中校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中校是自杀的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.80,0:09:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也有传闻说他们没有阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:10.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,藤堂中校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无论怎么说  照这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:21.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲小姐  卡莲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:24.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有点东西想给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该带她去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,客室  还是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去我的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦  说是你朋友  我还以为是男性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大清早回来不去上学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像还会进出贫民区呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趁着你父亲在本国就任意妄为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:48.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,血缘真是无可争辩的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.87,0:09:54.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,享受父亲不在时的逍遥是你才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:10:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办  该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:05.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  太太  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有靠女人身体这一个本钱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.41,0:10:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个复杂的家庭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.74,0:10:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要交给我的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷拜托我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.69,0:10:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,学园长?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.50,0:10:21.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中学以来的成绩证明书
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.67,0:10:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在学校不方便给你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:27.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是布里塔尼亚人和11区人混血这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.31,0:10:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那个是我的继母
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的母亲是打翻花瓶的那个迟钝女佣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.29,0:10:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲是修坦菲尔德的当家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.28,0:10:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲是一个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:50.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最后成了佣人被使唤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又没能力做什么工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算再怎么被看不起也只能傻乎乎地笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不用特地住在这个家里的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其实就是厚着脸皮的要住在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:03.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对着以前的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:05.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你讨厌你母亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是觉得麻烦而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.26,0:11:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是沉重的话题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.15,0:11:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正妻  外遇和女儿居然一起住这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.30,0:11:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也不完全是这样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:16.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,衣食住行也没有不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.85,0:11:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是…不能忍的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.50,0:11:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.19,0:11:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算每一个小事都能够忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:27.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果全都累积起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.57,0:11:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天会崩溃的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我很想要知道别人的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.43,0:11:36.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是没有说出去的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:55.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别在那种情况下哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:11:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个让人害羞的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.34,0:11:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请称这为直率
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:02.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过大家都得救了真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:04.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了黑色骑士团那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.22,0:12:08.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要逮捕犯罪者的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让警察来不就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.20,0:12:12.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他们为什么不这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:16.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是认为警察没法做到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:17.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,警察这种
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算现在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么去做警察  从内部改变不就行了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:23.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本来想要改变
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最后却被各种各样的规则束缚住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那只有等做了最大程度的努力去改变才能说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:34.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他们所作的只能说是独善
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.45,0:12:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,独善?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.89,0:12:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他们所说的恶到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.84,0:12:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以什么作为基准都不知道不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,单方面的自我满足而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你们两个人?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我走了  我一定要回军队去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:53.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回见  莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.47,0:12:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:08.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有空的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:13.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.38,0:13:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说一定要回军队去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那里是你的归处吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.39,0:13:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Refrain?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.54,0:13:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毒品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特征是让人觉得回到了过去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.48,0:13:28.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该很好卖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.69,0:13:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是对于日本人来说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.02,0:13:31.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都会怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被布里塔尼亚占领之前的日本
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是针对日本人的药物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能放着不管
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无赖的补给物资抵达了之后马上就行动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听说补给增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要成为同伴的人也有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:49.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色骑士团真是受欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.25,0:13:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是正义的朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弹药到了我再联系你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.80,0:13:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你倒是说点什么啊  你这个11区人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:14:00.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快道歉啊  道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,11区人不是很擅长低头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,11区人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.50,0:14:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对手有五个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:10.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不可能赢的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.69,0:14:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就能放着不管吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好好看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被打的那个11区人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.93,0:14:19.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,随便帮助他试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个11区人从明天起就没法做生意了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他是自己选择成为布里塔尼亚的奴隶的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:29.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在租界工作就是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.11,0:14:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.06,0:14:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有意见吗  你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,11区人很可怜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧  想成为他们的同伴吧  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:38.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.74,0:14:42.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也差不多厌倦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:44.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欺负11区人这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去游戏机厅么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.77,0:14:52.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:55.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是容易厌倦的家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.92,0:14:59.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.01,0:15:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.56,0:15:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要来一份加利福尼亚热狗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:10.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,男朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话  两位请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:14.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有冰淇淋哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.54,0:15:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,11区与还是日本的时候比起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以说是好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.61,0:15:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏成了布里塔尼亚的殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:24.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,军事也好经济也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:25.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都大幅的安定下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:27.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还能拿到市民权
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要到政府去办手续
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:32.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不就能成为名誉布里塔尼亚人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:33.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的就是自尊的问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.21,0:15:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  也能理解重视这个的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.78,0:15:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:40.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了这些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.95,0:15:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修·兰佩洛奇是怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.12,0:15:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的头脑似乎非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但总是口头上说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莎莉总是在惋惜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路不去努力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:54.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枉费头脑那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:15:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才什么都不做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:15:59.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的11区人也很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向布里塔尼亚人低头就能生活得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:10.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得你很帅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:11.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱着这种想法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.94,0:16:13.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看不起这个世界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:18.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对你这种想法抱有期待的我真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.30,0:16:20.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为你是个正经男人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个ORANGE事件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:34.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个枢木朱雀强夺事件的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.44,0:16:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卿说您没有记忆是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:42.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有指望你会相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我也在新宿那次事件中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,经历过丧失记忆的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.64,0:16:49.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.49,0:16:50.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恢复意识的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.27,0:16:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Sutherland已经被夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:55.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且在丧失记忆之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.50,0:16:57.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我遇见了一个穿学生服的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:16:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是说那个学生?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:01.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我记不起脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.65,0:17:04.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我认为有调查的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.84,0:17:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO那家伙在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说要打倒布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:12.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做的事不就是在帮警察嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是被人感谢的感觉并不坏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.19,0:17:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.37,0:17:18.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在网络已经是英雄了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.13,0:17:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样做真的就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:23.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:27.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:29.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真亏他能进去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:32.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,每一次都是  用的什么方法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,名古屋的部分搞定了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.50,0:17:41.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,租界里很安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.77,0:17:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色骑士团  参上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:53.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,KnightMare  怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.45,0:17:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:00.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,KnightMare果然很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.50,0:18:02.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有一架就有压倒性优势
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日本  日本
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  下个月就要结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.10,0:18:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,升职了  这次是去巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.58,0:18:18.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下个礼拜的烟花大会  一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我了  日本的技术是世界第一的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.82,0:18:22.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Refrain
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.39,0:18:26.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经确定了  去留学的事  我真行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果全都累积起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.61,0:18:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天会崩溃的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.86,0:18:32.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:34.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跑起来很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说直人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.70,0:18:51.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好好看着卡莲怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.47,0:18:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个女人是多么的弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,依赖布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:18:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,依赖男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.68,0:18:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次又是毒品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.89,0:19:01.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Knight Police?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.47,0:19:11.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是警察的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.72,0:19:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,串通在一起的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玉城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我调查的时候  的确是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:17.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.03,0:19:36.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.81,0:19:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲  直人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.82,0:19:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和KnightMare做对手的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:06.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快…逃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃  你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.90,0:20:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.91,0:20:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.81,0:20:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.98,0:20:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才一直待在那个家中的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:24.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只为了这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你真蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:37.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.35,0:21:01.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.37,0:21:03.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你能成为布里塔尼亚人了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.10,0:21:05.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.40,0:21:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就不会被打了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也能自由地打电话  去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是母亲…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.14,0:21:18.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虚伪的眼泪会伤害人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虚伪的笑容会伤害自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:27.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毒品的后遗症
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.56,0:21:29.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,基本无法进行对话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.71,0:21:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,需要时间才能康复
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.17,0:21:36.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,判决下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.55,0:21:37.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,二十年
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你等着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.91,0:21:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈出来之前我一定会改变给您看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.50,0:21:48.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我和妈妈能够正常生活的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.18,0:21:51.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  所以
