Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.02,0:21:59.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,加油  卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.34,0:22:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.28,0:22:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会加油
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.77,0:22:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会加油的
